{
    "code": "012", 
    "data": "\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t    It is reported through the source of Abdullah bin Abbas that once he went to the Masjidun Nabawee in the small hours of the night and saw Ali ibne Abi Talib (a.s.) praying Tahajjud Namaz. After the Namaz of watr, Maula Ali (a.s.) recited a Dua which Abdullah had never heard.\nIn reply to his question Ali ibn Abi Talib (a.s.) said:\n“Dua, I was reciting is Sanamay Quraysh. If someone recites this Dua sincerely, Almighty Allah will forgive him of his sins and fulfil his legitimate desires. Ibne Abbas remember that this Dua can also be recited to seek Almighty Allah’s help on behalf of any of your believing friends or relatives.”\nبِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ.\nBISMIL LAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM\nIn the name of Allah, the Beneficent, the Merciful.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ اٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ \nALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN.\nO  Allah! Send Your blessings upon Muhammad and the family of Muhammad\nاَللّٰهُمَّ الْعَنْ صَنَمَیْ قُرَیْشٍ وَ جِبْتَیْهَا وَ طَاغُوْتَیْهَا \nALLAAHUMMAL A’N SANAMAY QURAISHIN WA JIBTAYHAA WA TAAGHOOTAYHAA \nO  Allah! Curse the two idols of Quraish, and their two magicians, and their two tyrants,\nوَ اِفْكَیْهَا وَ ابْنَتَیْهَا \nWA IFQAYHAA WAB NATAYHEMAL \nand their two accusers of falsehood, and their two daughters,\nاللَّذَیْنِ خَالَفَا اَمْرَكَ وَ اَنْكَرَا وَحْیَكَ وَ جَحَدَا اِنْعَامَكَ \nLAZAYNE KHAALAFAA AMRAKA WA ANKARAA WAHYAKA WA JAHADAA INA’AMAKA \nthat opposed Your order, and denied Your revelation and rejected Your graces,\nوَ عَصَیَا رَسُوْلَكَ وَ قَلَّبَا دِیْنَكَ \nWA A’SAYAA RASOOLAKA WA QALLABAA DEENAKA \nand disobeyed Your Messenger, and destroyed Your religion, \nوَ حَرَّفَا کِتَابَكَ وَ اَحَبَّا اَعْدَآئَكَ \nWA HARRAFAA KETAABAKA WA AHABBA A-A’DAA-AKA\nand distorted Your Book, and loved Your enemies, \nوَ جَحَدَ اٰلَآئَكَ وَ عَطَّلَا اَحْكَامَكَ \nWA JAHADA AALAAA-AKA WA A’TTALAA AHKAAMAKA \nand negated Your Graciousness, and obstructed Your laws,\nوَ اَبْطَلَا فَرَآئِضَكَ وَ اَلْحَدَا فِیْ اٰیَاتِكَ \nWA ABTALAA FARAAA-EZAKA WA ALHADAA FEE AAYAATEKA \nand revocated Your obligations, and disbelieved in Your Signs,\nوَ عَادَیَا اَوْلِیَآئَكَ وَ وَالَیَا اَعْدَآئَكَ \nWA A’AADAYAA AWLEYAAA-AKA WA WAALAYAA A’ADAAA-AKA \nand antagonized Your Allies, and befriended Your enemies, \nوَ خَرَّبَا بِلاَدَكَ وَ اَفْسَدَا عِبَادَكَ \nWA KHARRABAA BELAADAKA WA AFSADAA E’BAADAKA \nand ruined Your cities, and corrupted Your servants.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ الْعَنْہُمَا وَ اَتْبَاعَہُمَا وَ اَوْلِیَآئَہُمَا \nALLAAHUMMAL A’NHOMAA WA ATBAA-A’HOMAA WA AWLEYAAA-AHOMAA\nO Allah! Cure them both and their admirers and their friends \nوَ اَشْیَاعَہُمَا وَ مُحِبِّیْهِمَا \nWA ASHYAA-A’HOMAA WA HOHIBBEEHEMAA\nand their followers and their lovers\nفَقَدْ اَخْرَبَا بَیْتَ النُّبُوَّۃِ \nFAQAD AKHRABAA BAYTAN NOBUWWATE \nfor they have ruined the house of Prophethood\nوَ رَدَمَا بَابَہٗ وَ نَقَضَا سَقْفَہٗ \nWA RADAMAA BAABAHU WA NAQAZAA SAQFAHU \nand closed its door, and broken its roof, \nوَ اَلْحَقَا سَمَائَہٗ بِاَرْضِهٖ وَ عَالِیَہٗ بِسَافِلِهٖ \nWA ALHAQAA SAMAAA-AHU BE-ARZEHI WA A’ALEYAHU BE-SAAFELEHI \nand brought down its elevated ceiling to its ground, and its height to a lower status,\nوَ ظَاهِرَہٗ بِبَاطِنِهٖ وَ اسْتَاْصَلاَ اَهْلَہٗ \nWA ZAAHERAHU BE-BAATENEHI WAS TAASALAA AHLAHU \nand its exterior to its interior, and destroyed its inhabitants, \nوَ اَبَادَ اَنْصَارَہٗ وَ قَتَلاَ اَطْفَالَہٗ \nWA ABADAA ANSAARAHU WA QATALAA ATFAALAHU \nand exiled their helpers, and killed their children, \nوَ اَخْلَیَا مِنْبَرَہٗ مِنْ وَ صِیِّهٖ وَ وَارِثِ عِلْمِهٖ \nWA AKHLAYAA MINBARAHU MIN WASIYYEHI WA WAARESE I’LMEHI\nand confiscated their pulpit from its successor and inheritor,\nوَ جَحَدَا اِمَامَتَہٗ وَ اَشْرَكَا بِرَبِّهِمَا \nWA JAHADAA EMAAMATAHU WA ASHRAKAA BERABBEHEMAA \nand negated the righteous leadership (Imamat) and ascribed a partner to their Lord, \nفَعَظِّمْ ذَنْبَہُمَا وَ خَلِّدْہُمَا فِیْ سَقَرَ \nFA-A’ZZIM ZAMBAHOMAA WA KHALLIDHOMAA FEE SAQARA \nso maximize their sins and make them abide forever in the bottom of Hell, \nوَ مَا اَدْرَاكَ مَا سَقَرَ لاَ تُبْقِیْ وَ لاَ تَذَرْ \nWA MAA ADRAAKA MAA SAQARA LAA TUBQEE WA LAA TAZAR\nAnd what will make you realize what the bottom of hell is? It leaves nothing nor spares anything. (The Holy Qur’an, 74:27-28)\nاَللّٰهُمَّ الْعَنْہُمْ بِعَدَدِ کُلِّ مُنْكَرٍ اَتَوْہُ \nALLAAHUMMAL A’NHUM BE-A’DADE KULLE MUNKARIN ATAWHO \nO Allah! Curse them by the number of each evil they have brought,\nوَحَقٍّ اَخْفَوْہُ وَ مِنْبَرٍ عَلَوْہُ وَ مُؤْمِنٍ اَرْجَوْہُ \nWA HAQQIN AKHFAWHO WA MINBARIN A’LAWHO WA MOAMENIN ARZAWHO\nand truth they have concealed, and pulpit they have ascended, and believers they have hurt, \nوَ مُنَافِقٍ وَّلَّوْہُ وَ وَلِیٍّ اٰذَوْہُ وَ طَرِیْدٍ اٰوَوْہُ \nWA MONAAFEQIN WALLAWHO WA WALIYYIN AAZAWHO WA TAREEDIN AAWAWHO \nand hypocrites they have befriended, and pious ones they have hurt, and rejected one in exile they have brought back, \nوَ صَادِقٍ طَرَدُوْہُ وَ كَافِرٍ نَصَرُوْہُ وَ اِمَامٍ قَهَرُوْہُ \nWA SAADEQIN TARADOOHO WA KAAFERIN NASAROOHO WA EMAAMIN QAHAROOHO \nand truthful ones they have exiled, and disbeliever they have supported, and Imam they have subjugated, \nوَ فَرْضٍ غَیَّرُوْہُ وَ اَثَرٍ اَنْكَرُوْہُ وَ شَرٍّ اٰثَرُوْہُ \nWA FARZIN GHAYYAROOHO WA ASARIN ANKAROOHO WA SHARRIN AASAROOHO \nand obligatory laws they have changed, and tradition they have denied, and evil they have authorized, \nوَ دَمٍ اَرَاقُوْہُ وَ خَیْرٍ بَدَّلُوْہُ وَ کُفْرٍ نَصَبُوْہُ \nWA DAMIN ARAQOOHO WA KHABARIN BADDALOOHO WA KUFRIN NASABOOHO\nand blood they have shed, and goodness they have changed, and disbelief they have established, \nوَ اِرْثٍ غَصَبُوْہُ وَ فَیْءٍ اقْتَطَعُوْہُ \nWA IRSIN GHASABOOHO WA FAY-ENIQ TATA-O’OHO \nand inheritance they have plundered, and booty they have prevented, \nوَ سُحْتٍ اَكَلُوْہُ وَ خُمْسٍ اسْتَحَلُّوْہُ \nWA SOHTIN AKALOOHO WA KHUMSENIS TAHALLOOHO \nand prohibited things they have consumed, and khums they have legalized (for themselves), \nوَ بَاطِلٍ اَسَّسُوْہُ وَ جَوْرٍ بَسَطُوْہُ وَ نِفَاقٍ اَسَرُّوْہُ \nWA BAATELIN ASSASOOHO WA JAWRIN BASATOOHO WA NEFAAQIN ASARROOHO \nand falsehood they have established, and cruelty they have practiced, and hypocrisy they have concealed,\nوَ غَدْرٍ اَضْمَرُوْہُ وَ ظُلْمٍ نَشَرُوْہُ وَ وَعْدٍ اَخْلَفُوْہُ \nWA GHADARIN AZAMAROOHO WA ZULMIN NASHAROOHO WA WA’DIN AKHLAFOOHO\nand treachery they have bored, and oppression they have spread, and promises they have dishonoured, \nوَ اَمَانَۃٍ خَانُوْہُ وَ عَهْدٍ نَقَضُوْہُ وَ حَلاَلٍ حَرَّمُوْہُ \nWA AMAANATIN KHAANOOHO WA A’HDIN NAQAZOOHO WA HALAALIN HARRAMOOHO \nand covenants they have broken, and lawful they prohibited, \nوَ حَرَامٍ اَحَلُّوْہُ وَ بَطْنٍ فَتَقُوْہُ وَ جَنِیْنٍ اَسْقَطُوْہُ \nWA HARAAMIN HALLALOOHO WA BATNIN FATAQOOHO WA JANEENIN ASQATOOHO\nand prohibited they have made lawful, and stomach they have ruptured, \nوَ ضِلْعٍ دَقُّوْہُ وَ صَكٍّ مَّزَّقُوْہُ \nWA ZIL-I’N DAQQOOHO WA SAKKIN MAZZAQOOHO \nand rib they have fractured, and document they tear apart, \nوَ شَمْلٍ بَدَّدُوْہُ وَ عَزِیْزٍ اَذَلُّوْہُ وَ ذَلِیْلٍ اَعَزُّوْہُ \nWA SHAMLIN BADDADOOHO WA A’ZEEZIN AZALLOOHO WA ZALEELIN A-A’ZZOOHO \nand unity they have dispersed, and honoured one they have degraded, and degraded one they have honoured, \nوَ حَقٍّ مَنَعُوْہُ وَ کِذْبٍ دَلَّسُوْہُ \nWA HAQQIN MANA-O’OHO WA KIZBIN DALLASOOHO\nand right they have prevented, and lies they have covered,\nوَ حُکْمٍ قَلَّبُوْہُ وَ اِمَامٍ خَالَفُوْہُ \nWA HUKMIN QALLABOOHO WA EMAAMIN KHAALAFOOHO \nand command they have altered, and Imam they have opposed.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ الْعَنْہُمْ بِکُلِّ اٰیَۃٍ حَرَّفُوْهَا \nALLAAHUMMAL A’NHOMAA BEKULLE AAYATIN HARRAFOOHO \nO Allah! Curse them for each (Quranic) verse they have distorted, \nوَ فَرِیْضَۃٍ تَرَکُوْهَا وَ سُنَّۃٍ غَیَّرُوْهَا \nWA FAREEZATIN TARAKOOHAA WA SUNNATIN GHAYYAROOHAA \nand obligation they have abandoned, \nوَ رُسُوْمٍ مَنَعُوْهَا وَ اَحْكَامٍ عَطَّلُوْهَا \nWA ROSOOMIN MANA-O’OHAA WA AHKAAMIN A’TTALOOHAA \nand tradition they have distorted, and (Divine) laws they forbade, \nوَ بَیْعَۃٍ نَكَثُوْهَا \nWA BAY-A’TIN NAKASOOHAA \nand the allegiance they have violated, \nوَ دَعْوٰى اَبْطَلُوْهَا وَ بَیِّنَۃٍ اَنْكَرُوْهَا \nWA DA’WAA ABTALOOHAA WA BAYYENATIN ANKAROOHAA \nand call they have invalidated, and evidence they have denied,\nوَ حِیْلَۃٍ اَحْدَثُوْهَا وَ خِیَانَۃٍ اَوْرَدُوْهَا \nWA HILYATIN AHDASOOHAA WA KHEYAANATIN AWRADOOHAA \nand crime they have committed, and betrayal they have performed, \nوَ عَقَبَۃٍ اِرْتَقُوْهَا وَ دِبَابٍ دَحْرَجُوْهَا \nWA A’QABATIN IRTAQOOHAA WA DEBAABIN DAH-RAJOOHAA \nand the hill they have climbed, and fixed rules they have changed, \nوَ اَزْیَافٍ لَزَمُوْهَا \nWA AZYAAFIN LAZAMOOHAA \nand the defects they have promoted,\nوَ شَهَادَاتٍ كَتَمُوْهَا وَ وَصِیَّۃٍ ضَیَّعُوْهَا \nWA SHA-HAADATIN KATAMOOHAA WA WASIYYATIN ZAYYA-O’OHAA \nand testimonies they have concealed, and advice they have made useless.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ الْعَنْہُمَا فِیْ مَکْنُوْنِ السِّرِّ وَ ظَاهِرِ الْعَلاَنِیَۃِ \nALLAAHUMMAL A’NHOMAA FEE MAKNOONIS SIRRE WA ZAAHERIL A’LAANEYATE \nO Allah! Curse those two secretly as well as openly, \nلَعْنًا کثِیْرًا اَبَدًا دَآئِمًا دَآئِبًا سَرْمَدًا \nLA’NAN KASEERAN ABADAN DAAA-EMAN DAAA-EBAN SARMADAN \na curse that is great in number, everlasting, abiding, persistent, eternal, \nلَا انْقِطَاعَ لِاَمَدِهٖ وَ لَا نَفَادَ لِعَدَدِهٖ \nLAN QETAA-A’ LE-AMADEHI WA LAA NAFAADA LE-A’DADEHI \nfor a limitless duration, for unlimited number of times and without any bounds. \nلَعْنًا یَغْدُوْا اَوَّلُہٗ وَ لَا يَرُوْحُ اٰخِرُہٗ لَہُمْ \nLA’NAN YAGHDOO AWWALOHU WA LAA YAROOHO AAKHEROHU LAHUM \nA curse that commences from the first one (of them) and continues after the last one of them \nوَ لِاَعْوَانِهِمْ وَ اَنْصَارِهِمْ وَ مُحِبِّیْهِمْ وَ مُوَالِیْهِمْ \nWA LE-AA’WAANEHIM WA ANSAAREHIM WA MOHIBBEEHIM WA MOWAALEEHIM \nand for their helpers, and their associates, and their lovers, and their friends, \nوَ الْمُسْلِمِیْنَ لَہُمْ وَ الْمَائِلِیْنَ اِلَیْهِمْ \nWAL MUSLEMEENA LAHUM WAL MAA-ELEENA ELAYHIM \nand their submitters and those who are inclined towards them, \nوَ النَّاهِضِیْنَ بِاِحْتِجَاجِهِمْ وَ الْمُقْتَدِیْنَ بِكَلاَمِهِمْ \nWAN NAAHEZEENA BE-EHTEJAAJEHIM WAL-MUQTADEENA BE-KALAAMEHIM \nand those stand with them in their protests and those who follow their words \nوَ الْمُصَدِّقِیْنَ بِاَحْكَامِهِمْ.\nWAL MOSADDEQEENA BE-AHKAAMEHIM.\nand those who approve their actions.\nThen say four times:\nاَللّٰهُمَّ عَذِّبْهُمْ عَذَاباً يَسْتَغِيْثُ مِنْهُ اَهْلُ النَّارِ \nALLAAHUMMA A’ZZIBHUM A’ZAABAN YASTAGHEESO MINHO AHLUN NAARE \nO Allah! Punish them a punishment that the people of Hell seek refuge from, \nآمِيْنَ رَبَّ الْعَالَمِيْنَ\nAAMEENA RABBAL A’ALAMEENA.\nSo be it, Lord of the Worlds.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    ", 
    "title": "Dua e Sanamay Quraish"
}